      "text": "for(int i = 0; i < arr.length; i++){\n if(map.containsKey(arr[i]){\n  map.put(arr[i], map.get(arr[i])+1);\n}else{\n map.put(arr[i],1);\n}\n} \n\nfor(Map.Entry<Integer,Integer> entry: map.entrySet()){\n if(entry.getValue > 1){\n   return true;\n}\n}\nreturn false;\n}\n ",
